            "event": "When searching for their first flat in Hyderabad after marriage, he spent three weekends meticulously visiting 14 properties, building spreadsheets comparing sq footage, builder reputation, and resale value, ultimately choosing a slightly smaller flat in a reputed complex over a cheaper but poorly constructed option.",
