                "content": "A defining moment in my life: When his son Arjun was born and developed a mild feeding issue at six weeks, he stayed up three nights cross-referencing medical journals and pediatrician forums before a single clinic visit, refusing to act on neighbors' home remedies. \u2014 Reinforced his analytical decision-making style and his deep trust in family over social circles \u2014 outside opinions, however well-meaning, carry little weight in his household decisions.",
