                "timestamp": "2026-04-04T06:59:24.561185Z",
                "type": "observation",
                "content": "A defining moment in my life: Shortly after her wedding, Priya discovered that a popular budget cooking oil brand she had been buying caused a mild but persistent digestive reaction in her husband, confirmed after methodically tracking their meals in a spreadsheet for three weeks. \u2014 This experience cemented her belief that cutting corners on food quality carries real health costs, hardwiring her quality-over-budget instinct even under moderate financial pressure.",
                "importance": 8,
                "emotional_valence": 0.0,
                "source_stimulus_id": null,
